the kitchen Welcome to the kitchen, this place isn't very fancy, nor simple. Most utensils and appliances are either wood or a cheap metal. They're all in places in which they're meant to be. There is no microwave, and the oven and stove are all useable by heat/fire. There is a sink near the stove, again very simple You will not find things that you can find in the #dinning-hall in here. It's mostly just things you can use to cook in here. Ingredients to cook are dotted around the room and organised so that you'll find things in similar food groups or catagories in the same place. In the back left corner there's a steal door to a fridge and freezer room where you'll find the things you'd typically find in your fridge and freezer. (edited)
